# sandhi RPC dialect test suite — carved out of tests/sandhi.tcyr at
# 1.2.8 to relieve the per-program-fixup-table cap (architecture/001).
# Covers the json builder + extractor, RPC dispatch err-envelope
# extraction, WebDriver URL/extract helpers, and MCP envelope shape.
# All 17 fns moved verbatim; sandhi.tcyr loses the corresponding
# `test_group(\"rpc/...\")` calls.

